title: Leaving jail, Puigdemont calls on Madrid to enter dialogue
text:
Leaving jail, Puigdemont calls on Madrid to enter dialogue 2:52pm BST - 01:02 
Former Catalan President Carles Puigdemont urged for the release of separatist leaders and called on Madrid to open a dialogue with the region as he left a German prison. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
